      <h1 class='title'>Departmental Report</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 15 May 2003 vol 405 c17WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_17ws' title='Col. 17WS &mdash; HC Deb 15 May 2003 vol 405 c17WS' name='column_17ws' href='#column_17ws' rel='bookmark'>17WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0405P0-05367'>
        <a name='S6CV0405P0_20030515_CWS_8'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-smith' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0405P0_20030515_CWS_8' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Smith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-smith" title="Mr Andrew Smith">The Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Andrew Smith)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0405P0-05367">I am today able to announce the publication of the Department for Work and Pensions Departmental Report. The report provides details of the Departments performance in 2002&#x2013;03 against its Public Service Agreement targets and sets out the Department's expenditure plans for 2003&#x2013;04 to 2005&#x2013;06. A copy has been placed in the Library.</p><p id="S6CV0405P0-05368"><table>
